quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  13,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  13,1,"a l- meem ray yeh kitaab Ellahi ki ayaat hain, aur jo kuch tumahray rab ki taraf se tum par nazil kya gaya hai woh ain haq hai, magar ( tumhari qoum ke ) aksar log maan nahi rahay hain"
  13,2,"woh Allah hi hai jis ne asmano ko aisay saharon ke baghair qaim kya jo tum ko nazar atay ho n, phir woh apne takhat saltanat par jalva farma howa, aur uss ne aftaab o Mahtab ko aik qanoon ka paband banaya iss saaray nizaam ki har cheez aik waqt muqarrar taq ke liye chal rahi hai aur Allah hi iss saaray kaam ki tadbeer farma raha hai woh nishanain khol khol kar bayan karta hai, shayad ke tum apne rab ki mulaqaat ka yaqeen karo"
  13,3,"aur wohi hai jis ne yeh zameen phela rakhi hai, is mein pahoron ke khontay garh rakhay hain aur darya baha diye hain usi ne har terhan ke phalon ke jore peda kiye hain, aur wohi din par raat taari karta hai un saari cheezon mein barri nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo ghhor o fikar se kaam letay hain"
  13,4,"aur dekho, zameen mein allag allag khittay paye jatay hain jo aik dosray se mut-tasil waqay hain angoor ke baagh hain, khityan hain, khajoor ke darakht hain jin mein se kuch akehray hain aur kuch dohray sab ko aik hi pani sairaab karta hai magar mazay mein hum kisi ko behtar bana dete hain aur kisi ko kamtar un sab cheezon mein bohat si nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo aqal se kaam letay hain"
  13,5,"ab agar tumhe taajjub karna hai to taajjub ke qabil logon ka yeh qoul hai ke"" jab hum mar kar matti ho jayen ge to kya hum naye suray se peda kiye jayen ge ?"" yeh woh log hain jinhon ne apne rab se kufar kya hai yeh woh log hain jin ki gardnon mein taoq parre hue hain yeh jahanumi hain aur jahannum mein hamesha rahen ge"
  13,6,yeh log bhalai se pehlay buraiee ke liye jaldi macha rahay hain halaank un se pehlay ( jo log is rawish par chalay hain un par khuda ke azaab ki ) Ibrat naak misalein guzar chuki hain haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera rab logon ki zayadtio ke bawajood un ke sath chasham poshi se kaam laita hai aur yeh bhi haqeeqat hai ke tera rab sakht saza dainay wala hai
  13,7,"yeh log jinhon ne tumhari ba t- maan-ne se inkaar kar diya hai, kehte hain ke"" iss shakhs par is ke rab ki taraf se koi nishani kyun nah utri? tum to mehez khabardaar kar dainay walay ho, aur har qoum ke liye aik rehnuma hai"
  13,8,Allah aik aik haamla ke pait se waaqif hai jo kuch is mein bantaa hai usay bhi woh jaanta hai aur jo kuch is mein kami ya Beshi hoti hai is se bhi woh bakhabar rehta hai har cheez ke liye uss ke haan aik miqdaar muqar rahay
  13,9,"woh posheeda aur zahir, har cheez ka aalam hai woh buzurag hai aur har haal mein baala tar rehne wala hai"
  13,10,"tum mein se koi shakhs khuwa zor se ba t- kere ya aahista, aur koi raat ki tareqi mein chhupa howa ho ya din ki roshni mein chal raha ho, is ke liye sab yaksaa hain"
  13,11,"har shakhs ke agay aur peechay is ke muqarrar kiye hue nigaran lagey hue hain jo Allah ke hukum se is ki dekh bhaal kar rahay hain haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah kisi qoum ke haal ko nahi badalta jab taq woh khud apne Awsaf ko nahi badal deti aur jab Allah kisi qoum ki shamat laane ka faisla kar le to phir woh kisi ke talaay nahi tal sakti, nah Allah ke muqablay mein aisi qoum ka koi haami o madad gaar ho sakta hai"
  13,12,wohi hai jo tumahray samnay bijliyan چمکاتا hai jinhein dekh kar tumhe andaishay bhi la-haq hotay hain aur umeeden bhi bandhatihain wohi hai jo pani se lde hue baadal uthata hai
  13,13,baadalon ki garaj is ki hamd ke sath is ki paki bayan karti hai aur farishtay is ki Haibat se leraztay hue uss ki tasbeeh karte hain woh karrktihui bijlion ko bhejta hai aur ( basa auqaat ) unhen jis par chahta hai ain is haalat mein gira deta hai jabkay log Allah ke baray mein jhagar rahay hotay hain fi al waqea is ki chaal barri zabardast hai
  13,14,"isi ko pukarna barhaq hai rahen woh doosri hastiyan jinhein is ko chore kar yeh log pukarte hain, woh unn ki duaon ka koi jawab nahi day sakteen unhen pukarna to aisa hai jaisay koi shakhs pani ki taraf haath phela kar uss se darkhwast kere ke to mere mun taq poanch ja, halaank pani uss taq pounchanay wala nahi bas aِsi terhan kafiroon ki duayen bhi kuch nahi hain magar aik teer be hadaf !"
  13,15,woh to Allah hi hai jis ko zameen o aasman ki har cheez touhan ا o karhan(marzi se ya majboori se) sajda kar rahi hai aur sab cheezon ke saaye subah o shaam uss ke agay jhukatey hain
  13,16,"inn se pucho, aasman o zameen ka rab kon hai? kaho, Allah phir un se kaho ke jab haqeeqat yeh hai to kya tum ne ussay chore kar aisay mabodon ko apna karsaaztehra liya jo khud apne liye bhi kisi naffa o nuqsaan ka ikhtiyar nahi rakhtay? kaho, kya andha aur aankhon wala barabar howa karta hai? kya roshni aur tarikhiyan yaksaa hoti hain? aur agar aisa nahi to kya inn tehra-ay hue sharikon ne bhi Allah ki terhan kuch peda kya hai ke uss ki wajah se inn par takhleeq ka maamla mushtaba ho gaya? kaho, har cheez ka khaaliq sirf Allah hai aur woh yaktaa hai, sab par ghalib !"
  13,17,Allah ne aasman se pani barsaya aur har nadi naala apne zarf ke mutabiq usay le kar chal nikla phir jab selaab utha to satah par jhaag bhi aa gay aur waisay hi jhaag unn dhaton par bhi uthte hain jinhein zewar aur bartan waghera bananay ke liye log pighlaya ا karte hain aِsi misaal se Allah haq aur baatil ke muamlay ko wazeh karta hai jo jhaag hai woh urr jaya karta hai aur jo cheez insanon ke liye nafea hai woh zameen mein tehar jati hai is terhan Allah misalon se apni baat samajhata hai
  13,18,"jin logon ne apne rab ki dawat qubool kar li hai unn ke liye bhalai hai aur jinhon ne usay qubool nah kya woh agar zameen ki saari doulat ke bhi maalik hon aur itni hi aur faraham kar len to woh khuda ki pakar se bachney ke liye is sab ko Fidya mein day daalnay par taya ray ho jayen ge yeh woh log hain jin se buri terhan hisaab liya jaye ga aur unn ka thikana jahannum hai, bohat hi bura thikana"
  13,19,"bhala yeh kis terhan mumkin hai ke woh shakhs jo tumahray rab ki iss kitaab ko jo is ne tum par nazil ki hai haq jaanta hai, aur woh shakhs jo is haqeeqat ki taraf se andha hai, dono yaksaa ho jayen? nasiyaat to Danish mand log hi qubool kya karte hain"
  13,20,"aur unn ka tarz amal yeh hota hai ke Allah ke sath apne ehad ko poora karte hain, ussay mazboot bandhnay ke baad toar nahi daaltay"
  13,21,"unn ki rawish yeh hoti hai ke Allah ne jin jin rawabit ko barqarar rakhnay ka hukum diya hai inhen barqarar rakhtay hain, apne rab se drtay hain aur is baat ka khauf rakhtay hain ke kahin un se buri terhan hisaab nah liya jaye"
  13,22,"unn ka haal yeh hota hai ke apne rab ki Raza ke liye sabr se kaam letay hain, namaz qaim karte hain, hamaray diye hue rizaq mein se alania aur posheeda kharch karte hain, aur buraiee ko bhalai se dafaa karte hain akhirat ka ghar unhi logon ke liye hai"
  13,23,yani aisay baagh jo unn ki abdi qiyam gaah hon ge woh khud bhi un mein daakhil hon ge aur un ke abao ajdaad aur unn ki biwion aur unn ki aulaad mein se jo jo Saleh hain woh bhi unn ke sath wahan jayen ge mulaika har taraf se unn ke istaqbaal ke liye ayen ge
  13,24,"aur unn se kahin ge ke"" tum par salamti hai, tum ne duniya mein jis terhan sabr se kaam liya uss ki badolat aaj tum iss ke mustahiq hue ho"" pas kya hi khoob hai yeh akhirat ka ghar !"
  13,25,"rahay woh log jo Allah ke ehad ko mazboot bandh lainay ke baad toar daaltay hain, jo unn rabton ko kaatetay hain jinhein Allah ne jornay ka hukum diya hai, aur jo zameen mein fasaad pheilatay hain, woh laanat ke mustahiq hain aur un ke liye akhirat mein bohat bura thikana hai"
  13,26,"Allah jis ko chahta hai rizaq ki farakhi bakhshta hai aur jisay chahta hai ke npa tala rizaq deta hai yeh log dunewi zindagi mein magan hain, halaank daal naya ki zindagi akhirat ke muqablay mein aik Mataa qaleel ke siwa kuch bhi nahi"
  13,27,"yeh log jinhon ne ( risalat Muhammad iSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ko maan-ne se ) inkaar kar diya hai kehte hain"" iss shakhs par iss ke rab ki taraf se koi nishani kyun nah utri"" kaho, Allah jisay chahta hai gumraah kar deta hai aur woh apni taraf anay ka rasta usi ko dekhata hai jo uss ki taraf rujoo kere"
  13,28,aisay hi log hain woh jinhon ne ( iss nabi ki dawat ko ) maan liya aur unn ke dilon ko Allah ki yaad se itminan naseeb hota hai khabardaar raho! Allah ki yaad hi woh cheez hai jis se dilon ko itminan naseeb howa karta hai
  13,29,phir jin logon ne dawat haq ko maana aur naik amal kiye woh khush naseeb hain aur un ke liye acha injaam hai
  13,30,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, aِsi shaan se hum ne tum ko rasool bana kar bheja hai, aik aisi qoum mein jis se pehlay bohat si qoumain guzar chuki hain, taakay tum inn logon ko woh pegham sunaaoo jo hum ne tum par nazil kya hai, iss haal mein ke yeh apne nihayat meharban khuda ke kafir banay hue hain inn se kaho ke wohi mera rab hai, uss ke siwa koi mabood nahi hai, usi par mein ne bharosa kya aur wohi mera Malja o mava hai"
  13,31,"aur kya ho jata agar koi aisa quran utaar diya jata jis ke zor se pahar chalne lagtay, ya zameen shaqq ho jati, ya murdy qabron se nikal kar bolnay lagtay? ( is terhan ki nishanain dikha dena kuch mushkil nahi hai ) balkay sara ikhtiyar hi Allah ke haath mein hai phir kya ahal imaan ( abhi taq kufar ki talab ke jawab mein kisi nishani ke zahuur ki aas laga ye baithy hain aur woh yeh jaan kar ) mayoos nahi ho gay ke agar Allah chahta to saaray insanon ko hadaayat day deta? jin logon ne khuda ke sath kufar ka rawayya ikhtiyar kar ray kha hai unn par un ke krtoton ki wajah se koi nah koi aafat aati hi rehti hai, ya un ke ghar ke qareeb kahin nazil hoti hai yeh silsila chalta rahay ga yahan taq ke Allah ka wada aan poora ho yaqeenan Allah apne waday ki khilaaf warzi nahi karta"
  13,32,"tum se pehlay bhi bohat se Rasolo-n ka mazaq uraya ja chuka hai, magar mein ne hamesha munkir yan ko dheel di aur aakhir-kaar un ko pakar liya, phir dekh lau ke meri saza kaisi sakht thi"
  13,33,"phir kya woh jo aik aik mutnaqas ki kamaai par nazar rakhta hai ( uss ke muqablay mein yehjasartain ki ja rahi hain ke ) logon ne uss ke kuch shareektehra rakhay hain? ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho ( agar waqai woh khuda ke apne banaye hue shareek hain to ) zara unn ke na meem lau ke woh kon hain? kya tum Allah ko aik nai baat ki khabar day rahay ho jisay woh apni zameen mein nahi jaanta? ya tum log bas yuhin jo mun mein aata hai keh daaltay ho? haqeeqat yeh hai ke jin logon ne dawat haq ko maan-ne se inkaar kya hai un ke liye unn ki makaryan khushnuma bana di gayi hain aur woh raah raast se rok diye gay hain, phir jis ko Allah gumraahi mein pheink day ussay koi raah dikhaane wala nahi hai"
  13,34,"aisay logon ke liye duniya ki zindagi hi mein azaab hai, aur akhirat ka azaab uss se bhi ziyada sakht hai koi aisa nahi jo unhen khuda se bachanay wala ho"
  13,35,"khuda taras insanon ke liye jis jannat ka wada kya gaya hai is ki shaan yeh hai ke is ke neechay nehrein beh rahi hain, is ke phal daimi hain aur is ka saya la zawaal yeh injaam hai mut-taqi logon ka aur munkareen haq ka injaam yeh hai ke un ke liye dozakh ki aag hai"
  13,36,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, jin logon ko hum ne pehlay kitaab di thi woh iss kitaab se jo hum ne tum par nazil ki hai, khush hain aur mukhtalif garohoon mein kuch log aisay bhi hain jo is ki baaz baton ko nahi mantay tum saaf keh do ke"" mujhe to sirf Allah ki bandagi ka hukum diya gaya hai aur is se mana kya gaya hai ke kisi ko is ke sath shareektehraؤں lehaza mein isi ki taraf dawat deta hon aur isi ki taraf mera rujoo hai """
  13,37,aِsi hadaayat ke sath hum ne yeh farmaan arabi tum par nazil kya hai ab agar tum ne iss ilm ke bawajood jo tumahray paas aa chuka hai logon ki khwahisaat ki pairwi ki to Allah ke muqablay mein nah koi tumhara haami o madadgaar hai aur nah koi is ki pkarr se tum ko bacha sakta hai
  13,38,tum se pehlay bhi hum bohat se rasool bhaij chuke hain aur unn ko hum ne biwi bachon wala hi banaya tha aur kisi rasool ki bhi yeh taaqat nah thi ke Allah ke azan ke baghair koi nishani khud laa dekhata har daur ke liye aik kitaab hai
  13,39,"Allah jo kuch chahta hai mita deta hai aur jis cheez ko chahta hai qaim rakhta hai, umm al-kitab usi ke paas hai"
  13,40,"aur ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, jis buray injaam ki dhamki hum inn logon ko day rahay hain uss koi hissa khuwa hum tumahray jeetay jee dikha den ya is ke zahuur mein anay se pehlay hum tumhe utha len, bahar haal tumhara kaam sirf pegham pouncha dena hai aur hisaab lena hamara kaam hai"
  13,41,"kya yeh log dekhte nahi hain ke hum iss sarzamen par chalay aa rahay hain aur is ka daira har taraf se tang karte chalay atay hain? Allah hukoomat kar raha hai, koi is ke faislon par nazar sani karne o ila nahi hai, aur ussay hisaab letay kuch der nahi lagti"
  13,42,"inn se pehlay jo log ho guzray hain woh bhi barri barri chaalein chal chuke hain, magar asal faisla kin chaal to poori ki poori Allah hi ke haath mein hai woh jaanta hai ke kon kya kuch kamaai kar raha hai, aur anqareeb yeh munkareen haq dekh len ge ke injaam kis ka bakhair hota hai"
  13,43,"yeh munkareen kehte hain ke tum khuda ke beje hue nahi ho kaho"" mere aur tumahray darmain Allah ki gawahi kaafi hai aur phir har uss shakhs ki gawahi jo kitaab aasmani ka ilm rakhta hai """
